{"TopicId":140131,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"LaytheDragon\u0026#039;s Sunflare(s)","CreatedByName":"LaytheDragon","CreatedById":149656,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-19T22:25:03Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"LaytheDragon","CreatedById":149656,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-19T22:25:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EThis is a thread for my alternate sunflare mod(s) for scatterer. So far, it seems likely that sci-fi-themed flares are what I may/will post (despite not using them myself), since they are quite easy to create simplistic flares for, and there are fewer options for them posted as of yet.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTripartite Rays Sunflare:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022V2erMQe.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022564\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/V2erMQe.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003EA simplistic, sci-fi-themed sunflare, the Tripartite Rays sunflare may please your eyes with its triangular rays of radiation.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ETo install:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDrag all the contents of the \u0022Tripartite Rays Flare\u0022 folder (but not the folder itself) within .zip file from download into the \u0022GameData/scatterer/sunflare\u0022 folder, replacing the original contents of that folder\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs for any sunflare mod, it is a good idea (but not necessary) to backup the previous sunflare (previous contents of \u0022GameData/scatterer/sunflare\u0022 in KSP directory) before installation\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/103963-wip112-scatterer-atmospheric-scattering-v00246-08052016-fixed-terrain-shadows/\u0026amp;page=181\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003ERequires Scatterer Mod\u003C/a\u003E ( \u0026lt;---- Thread)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://spacedock.info/mod/707/Tripartite%20Rays%20Sunflare?ga=%3CGame\u002B3102\u002B%27Kerbal\u002BSpace\u002BProgram%27%3E\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EDownload Tripartite Rays H\u003C/a\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://spacedock.info/mod/707/Tripartite%20Rays%20Sunflare?ga=%3CGame\u002B3102\u002B%27Kerbal\u002BSpace\u002BProgram%27%3E\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Eere: The download link (on spacedock)\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Note that the description here is basically that which is found on Spacedock)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Chr\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"daniel l.","CreatedById":57763,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-23T23:41:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022d4157dcc2c693bc717d43b6e7ea16be3_200x200\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://img.phone.baidu.com/public/uploads/store_9/d/4/1/d4157dcc2c693bc717d43b6e7ea16be3_200x200.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUmmm...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-23T23:41:19Z\u0022 title=\u002205/23/2016 11:41  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 23, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by daniel l.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceKraken","CreatedById":130353,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-25T17:48:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222598043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022140131\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221464046872\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257763\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022daniel l.\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 23.05.2016 at 3:41 AM, daniel l. said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022d4157dcc2c693bc717d43b6e7ea16be3_200x200\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://img.phone.baidu.com/public/uploads/store_9/d/4/1/d4157dcc2c693bc717d43b6e7ea16be3_200x200.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUmmm...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI need illuminati version. NOW!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LaytheDragon","CreatedById":149656,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-25T23:25:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222600850\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022140131\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221464198532\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130353\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpaceKraken\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, SpaceKraken said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI need illuminati version. NOW!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUh... I could probably do that for the sunFlare, and also add luminous green sunSpikes (also part of the flare), or do the opposite, but what about the ghosts (the glares, separate from the flare itself)? Translucent money-green triangles? The words \u0022Illuminati Confirmed\u0022? Both? Give me more details on what is requested for the ghosts, and this may become a real sun flare for download by/during/after the weekend. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"daniel l.","CreatedById":57763,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-09T00:00:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes please do an illuminati sunflare! Im gonna do a lord Gaben sunflare. Since his face is our light and soul \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u00A0And maybe a skybox to match\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LaytheDragon","CreatedById":149656,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-20T02:44:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222623131\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022140131\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221465430438\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257763\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022daniel l.\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/8/2016 at 8:00 PM, daniel l. said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes please do an illuminati sunflare! Im gonna do a lord Gaben sunflare. Since his face is our light and soul \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u00A0And maybe a skybox to match\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57763-daniel-l/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002257763\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/57763-daniel-l/\u0022 rel=\u0022external\u0022\u003E@daniel l.\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Oops, I didn\u0027t notice this post due to a lack of a notification! Next weekend maybe shall I create it? Or if I have time in between.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI still would like to know what \u0022ghost\u0022 (the glare triangles coming towards the center of the screen from the Sun, like the semi-transparent blue triangles seen in the picture in my signature) designs should be used. Miniature green triangles? Multiple of the miniature green illuminati all seeing eye? The words \u0022Illuminati Confirmed\u0022? I can create it\u00A0quicker if I know what to make the ghosts as. I may or may not also release another sci-fi sunflare along with it, too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-20T02:45:17Z\u0022 title=\u002206/20/2016 02:45  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 20, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by LaytheDragon\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"daniel l.","CreatedById":57763,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-20T06:10:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u002